issue.title: Firebase Data
issue.body:
### Context
We will need a way to display the deli's on our map to target places close to the user

### Description
I created a database with the data from NYC Open Data with information about different food concessions in firebase. I then grab this data from the database and map it to our Map from it's longitude and latitude.

issue.title: f/google map
issue.body:
### Context
In order to display where nearby deli's and food carts are, we will need a map. 

### Description
This ticket initializes a map. I used `react-google-maps` (https://github.com/tomchentw/react-google-maps) to quickly incorporate a map into our project. I centered the map around NYC and gave it a dark theme.
